                            <comment id="159458" author="yong.fan" created="Thu, 21 Jul 2016 08:00:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;These sanity-scrub test_4b/test_4c failures should be retailed with the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7782&quot; title=&quot;sanity-scrub test_2: NULL pointer dereference at 0x10 in lu_context_key_get() on mds2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7782&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7782&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/18801/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/18801/&lt;/a&gt;. That has been reverted. I will work on that and fix related issue in such ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="159389" author="jamesanunez" created="Wed, 20 Jul 2016 19:21:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This test failure started to fail in autotest on July 13, 2016 and may be related to the patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/18801&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/18801&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7782&quot; title=&quot;sanity-scrub test_2: NULL pointer dereference at 0x10 in lu_context_key_get() on mds2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7782&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7782&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; scrub: handle slave obj of striped directory&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
